The input file is made as follows

***********input.dat****************
N
concentration for B
Temperature
Euu(both up spin)
Edd(both down spin)
Edu(up and down spin)
************************************

***********INSTRUCTIONS****************
just use
./run.sh
to compile,run and main.c and to see a plot of the profiles

***********RESULTS****************
like spins start to couple together and large domains of UP and DOWN spins are observed
